        "id": 1099352
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-06-13T17:19:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There may be a bug here.  In the old code, it seems like kMaxVertexAttributes is really kind of misnamed: it\u0027s used as a default, and nothing ever enforces that it\u0027s the max.  You could call the GLDecoderContextData with numLocaions \u003d 128, for example.  Use of the fixed-size std::Array really does make it a max.\n\nSo it seems to me that you either have to go back to the old use of a vector, or convince me that the old code could have asserted in the constructor that numLocations \u003c\u003d kMaxVertexAttributes.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 71,
        "startChar": 34,
        "endLine": 71,
        "endChar": 54
      },
      "revId": "1c55b09cb0c861febdac06ad9e533fbae33addce",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "8f09f4df_84018731",
        "filename": "distrib/android-emugl/shared/OpenglCodecCommon/GLDecoderContextData.h",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 71,
      "author": {
        "id": 1082465
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-06-13T17:44:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That could be a good idea, but I think the situation right now is that kMaxVertexAttributes (64) is \u003e\u003e GL_MAX_VERTEX_ATTRIBS in any situations with existing GPU hardware. So far it looks like it\u0027s just 16 all the time, and most apps really use like 4. These vertex attributes are used to assign different abstract coordinates to vertices like position, color, normal, texture coordinate (there we go, 4). You might be using multiple sets of texture coordinates if you are doing fancy blending work, but never anything close to or above 16 AFAIK.\n\nStrictly speaking, yeah the max vertex attributes could be so high that we\u0027d need to update kMaxVertexAttributes, but that situation hasn\u0027t shown up at all. Plus, we only call the GLDecoderContextData ctor with kMaxVertexAttributes.",
      "parentUuid": "8f09f4df_2fecd9fc",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 71,
        "startChar": 34,
        "endLine": 71,
        "endChar": 54
      },
      "revId": "1c55b09cb0c861febdac06ad9e533fbae33addce",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "8f09f4df_84b3474d",
        "filename": "distrib/android-emugl/shared/OpenglCodecCommon/GLDecoderContextData.h",
